Besides, designing a TVC mount for a cluster of 4 engines with the diameter of a Klima C2 compromises space inside the fuselage and so its functionality.
After evaluating cost per test, proο§¹le ο§²ight, delay ignition magnitude and design reliability of the TVC, the Klima D9 (case 1) has been stated to have the best probability to success. Therefore the one selected to continue under the investigation.

